<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Service Mesh - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/service-mesh/</link><description>Service Mesh - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/service-mesh/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Service Mesh</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%BA%91%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/service-mesh/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%BA%91%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/service-mesh/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="service-mesh">Service Mesh</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Service Mesh通过Sidecar代理将服务间通信从业务代码中剥离，实现流量治理、安全通信和可观测性的基础设施化，是微服务治理的演进方向。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="service-mesh通过sidecar代理统一接管服务间流量在业务无感知的情况下实现治理与观测">Service Mesh通过Sidecar代理统一接管服务间流量，在业务无感知的情况下实现治理与观测</h2>
<h3 id="核心架构">核心架构</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">传统微服务                        Service Mesh
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">业务A ←→ 业务B                    业务A → Sidecar → Sidecar → 业务B
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓  服务发现/熔断/重试               ↑         ↑         ↑
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓  负载均衡/链路追踪             (治理能力下沉到基础设施层)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓  全写在业务代码里</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>组件</th>
          <th>职责</th>
          <th>代表产品</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>数据面</td>
          <td>Sidecar代理，实际转发流量</td>
          <td>Envoy、Linkerd-proxy</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>控制面</td>
          <td>配置下发、证书管理、策略控制</td>
          <td>Istio、Linkerd、Consul</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="核心能力">核心能力</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>能力</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>配置方式</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>流量路由</td>
          <td>按版本/权重/Header分发</td>
          <td>VirtualService</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>灰度发布</td>
          <td>金丝雀、蓝绿部署</td>
          <td>流量比例控制</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>熔断降级</td>
          <td>失败率/慢请求触发熔断</td>
          <td>DestinationRule</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>超时重试</td>
          <td>自动重试与超时控制</td>
          <td>路由规则</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>mTLS</td>
          <td>服务间自动双向TLS</td>
          <td>PeerAuthentication</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>可观测性</td>
          <td>自动生成指标、日志、追踪</td>
          <td>无需埋点</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
